(856, 0, 0, 'tech', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Reverse 820mm', 'datas/thumbs/1-reversebar1.jpg', 'Egy kis rövid tech infó a Revers túlméretezett kormányáról a Revers 820mm-rõl.\r\n\r\n    * The 820mm bars far exceed the EN handle bar test.\r\n    * The Solid World Cup team reported that the wider bars utilised power from the shoulders more and less from the arms, making arm pump less noticable on long tracks.\r\n    * Some riders were fitting extensions to the 760mm bars, proving that some wanted even wider bars.\r\n    * The full 820mm maybe just for the real tall/broad shouldered rider, but you can cut them down to 800 or less to suit.\r\n    * Cost in Germany is 79,90€\r\n    * Available end of March beginning of April.\r\n\r\nReverse Triple X Handlebars b Reverse 820mm Bars\r\n\r\n[img_border_f]datas/users/1-reversebar1.jpg[/img_border_f]', NULL, '', 1, 1265219763, 1265219640, 1296755640, 0, '', '', 43, 0.00, 0, ''),
(866, 0, 0, 'news', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Cedric a Santa Cruz-nál', 'datas/thumbs/1-cedric.jpg', '[colleft][thumb=datas/thumbs/1-cedric.jpg]1-cedric.jpg[/thumb][/colleft]Megjött a legfrissebb CG Newsletter, melyben beszámol arról, hogy a brigádot a Santa Cruz fogja ellátni vázzal, mely a jó öreg V10-es lesz. A tovább után az angol hírlevél is megtekinthetõ. [more]\r\n\r\n    CG RACING BRIGADE news 10/02/10\r\n\r\n    Now it''s the right time ! : )\r\n\r\n    I know a lot of people have been waiting for this newletter for a long time !\r\n\r\n    I have the pleasure and the honor to introduce my new bike sponsor !\r\n\r\n    The CG RACING BRIGADE is going to be pimped on SANTA CRUZ bikes.\r\n\r\n    Thanks to SANTA CRUZ to trust in me and the BRIGADE for the future; I am happy and proud to ride the V10.\r\n\r\n    I know I am going to have all the keys in my hand to do a killer job.\r\n\r\n    See you guys to the next event with my new bikes and other partners to celebrate some good moment with the BRIGADE.\r\n\r\n    Special thanks to all the fans who support me by e-mails and on FACEBOOK !\r\n\r\n    As I say, The BRIGADE is coming !\r\n\r\n    CG\r\n\r\n     \r\n\r\n    "Santa Cruz Bicycles is very excited to be the frame supplier for Cedric Gracia''s Racing Brigade. There are few riders who are competitive in multiple disciplines these days, especially one''s that have a great attitude and personality such as Cedric. We look forward to helping Cedric achieve his goals".\r\n\r\n    Rob ROSKOPP', NULL, '', 1, 1265898758, 1265898540, 1297434540, 0, '', '', 26, 0.00, 0, ''),
